  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced sausage and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onions and bell peppers and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the diced potatoes and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Push the potato and sausage mixture to one side of the skillet.",
    "Pour the beaten eggs into the empty side of the skillet and scramble them until cooked through.",
    "Mix the eggs with the potato and sausage mixture.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
